---
source: crates/speedrun/src/help.rs
expression: output
---
      ┌──────────────── Keybindings ────────────────┐       
      │ Playback                                    │       
      │   Space         Play / pause                │       
      │   + / =         Speed up                    │       
      │   -             Speed down                  │       
      │                                             │       
      │ Navigation                                  │       
      │   ← →           Seek ±5s                    │       
      │   Shift+← →     Seek ±30s                   │       
      │   . ,           Step forward / back         │       
      │   0-9           Jump to 0%-90%              │       
      │   Home / g      Jump to start               │       
      │   End / G       Jump to end                 │       
      │                                             │       
      │ Markers                                     │       
      │   ] [           Next / prev marker          │       
      │   -m            Auto-pause at markers (CLI) │       
      │                                             │       
      │ Search                                      │       
      │   /             Search                      │       
      │   n             Next match                  │       
      │   N             Previous match              │       
      │   Esc           Clear search                │       
      │                                             │       
      │ Display                                     │       
      │   Tab           Toggle controls             │       
      │   ?             Toggle help                 │       
      │                                             │       
      │ Application                                 │       
      └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘
